        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Because of the dynamic nature of Python classes, doing this unconditionally might break Python compatibilty. I would rather to it as opt-in: some directive to do it for all classes for `__slots__` and for every class which is already declared as `cdef class`.",
